#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:316
#, php-format
msgid "Only for “Direct OpenAI API”. Get your API key from <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">OpenAI Platform</a>. You can also define WE_SPAMFIGHTER_OPENAI_KEY in wp-config.php."
msgstr "Nur für „Direct OpenAI API“. API-Schlüssel auf der <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">OpenAI Platform</a> erstellen. Alternativ WE_SPAMFIGHTER_OPENAI_KEY in wp-config.php definieren."%s\" target=\"_blank\">OpenAI Platform</a> erstellen. Alternativ WE_SPAMFIGHTER_OPENAI_KEY in wp-config.php definieren.\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">OpenAI Platform</a> erstellen. Alternativ WE_SPAMFIGHTER_OPENAI_KEY in wp-config.php definieren."

